msgctxt "unified_islam코0"
msgid "A United Islam"
msgstr "통합된 이슬람"

msgctxt "desc_unified_islam코0"
msgid ""
"The People of Islam are united and are forgetting their internal differences "
"in favor of a merciful nation."
msgstr "하나의 자비로운 국가에 찬성하여 이슬람의 백성들이 내부의 차이를 잊어버리고 하나가 되었다."

msgctxt "change_religion_sunni_title코0"
msgid "Change Religion to Sunni"
msgstr "수니파로 개종하자"

msgctxt "change_religion_sunni_desc코0"
msgid ""
"The difference between the Sunni and the Shiite is that the Sunni believes "
"that the first four caliphs - Mohammed's successors - rightfully took his "
"place as the leaders of Muslims. Meanwhile, the Shiites believe that only "
"the heirs of the fourth caliph, Ali, are the legitimate successors of "
"Mohammed."
msgstr ""
"수니파와 시아파의 차이점은 수니파의 경우 무함마드의 계승자인 첫 4대의 칼리프가 무슬림의 지도자로서 자리를 확실히 했다고 믿는 반면, "
"시아파는 오직 4대 칼리프인 알리의 후손들만이 적법한 무함마드의 계승자라고 믿는 것이다."

msgctxt "change_religion_shiite_title코0"
msgid "Change Religion to Shiite"
msgstr "시아파로 개종하자"

msgctxt "change_religion_shiite_desc코0"
msgid ""
"The Shiites believe that only the heirs of the fourth caliph, Ali, are the "
"legitimate successors of Mohammed while the Sunni believes that the first "
"four caliphs - Mohammed's successors - rightfully took his place as the "
